item.title: Consultancy
item.description: Buying a house can be stressful, and there are a lot of costs involved throughout the buying process. These costs add up, and if you invest in the wrong house it can be hard to recover all the loses. The best way you can lower your chances of making a bad investment is to research the house beforehand. We are here to make that process stress free. We charge a flat fee of $300 for our services.
